https://wiki.jenkins-ci.org/display/JENKINS/Step+by+step+guide+to+set+up+master+and+slave+machines

Add Slave
1. go the jenkins web manager => New Node
2. Remote FS root: /home/jenkins/
3. Launch method ssh
   remember fill the username and passwd
4. login to slave mechine
5. wget http://yourserver:port/jnlpJars/slave.jar
6. java -jar slave.jar -jnlpUrl http://yourserver:port/computer/slave-name/slave-agent.jnlp
   Make sure to replace "slave-name" with the name of slave.
7. add user jenkins
   his home is /home/jenkins
   set jenkins:jenkins own
8. go the jenkins web manager to start the slave

